  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a developer, I want to integrate Status with NFC Card **so that** private keys and seed phrase will be stored outside the smartphone, offline and encrypted on NFC Card. \r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: Sync new card, authorize send cryptocurrency, authorize login, backup card\r\n[comment]: Login, withdrawal\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n[comment]: # The card will be optional, use the NFC Card who wants more privacy and security.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\n[comment]: # It is very easy, I already have the code on dart and node.js.\r\n",
